Standardize output file naming format -- name sympy and pytables tests the same way we do theano


Check whether we need to use os.walk for sympy or pytables tests


Install optional backends for matplotlib (latex etc.)


.matplotlibrc to use Agg by default


Set up ramdisk for theano cache during Salt provisioning:

mount -t ramfs -o size=200m ramfs /home/vagrant/theano_ram_cache

Then get Theano to use this during testing:

THEANO_FLAGS="base_compiledir=/home/vagrant/theano_ram_cache" $PYTHON `which theano-nose` --theano

